      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/sqa-level1",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R2) is commercially validated and operated under a documented quality management system. Version control, input file archiving, and run-log traceability are maintained throughout the study. SQA level 2 achieved against a required level of 1 for MRL 2."
