      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/code-verification-level1",
      "rationale": "The solver has been verified against canonical benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity flow and Poiseuille flow. Published verification reports from ANSYS and independent FDA CDRH CFD benchmarking exercises confirm solver correctness for incompressible viscous flows. Achieved level 2 exceeds required level 1."
