      "rationale": "At MRL 2 with a commercially validated solver operating within its verified operating envelope, explicit solver error characterization beyond code verification is not required. The solver residual convergence criterion (1e-6 for all equations) and double-precision arithmetic are documented in the simulation protocol. Scoped out per MRL 2 guidance with documented justification."
    },
    {
