      "rationale": "Use error risk is mitigated through documented simulation protocols, peer review of all CFD setups by a second qualified analyst, and checklist-based pre-run verification. At MRL 2, formal use error factor assessment beyond these procedural controls is not mandated. Scoped out with documented procedural mitigations in place."
    },
    {
