      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model and power-law hemolysis damage accumulation model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) were selected based on published literature supporting their applicability to blood pump flows. Model form uncertainty is partially addressed through the output comparison factor. Formal model form factor assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 given the available validation evidence and literature precedent."
